name: Exuberance No. 2 Cobalt Blue and Mint
description:
Reach for the stars, and the celestial heavens will open wide; Exuberance No. 2 Cobalt Blue and Mint create cosmic kinetic energy.
Exuberance No. 2 Cobalt Blue and Mint is a one-of-a-kind artistic collaboration that intertwines Tery Spataro's flower photographs and the artificial intelligence of Playform.io to give life to this transfixing new creation. The Exuberance art series are physical surface designs.
